dct_description_sm: Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. At head of title: Atlantic Ocean. "J. & C. Walker, Sculpt."--Lower right margin. "Published according to Act of Parliament ... July 26th 1849." "Soundings in fathoms, figures on the land show height in feet." "[Chart] 1950"--Lower right margin.
dct_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
